<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img src="//s0.wp.com/latex.php?latex=F_n+%3D+%5Cdfrac+1%7B%5Csqrt+5%7D%5CBig%28%5CBig%28%5Cdfrac%7B1%2B%5Csqrt+5%7D2+%5CBig%29%5En+-+%5CBig%28%5Cdfrac%7B1-%5Csqrt+5%7D2+%5CBig%29%5En%5CBig%29+%5C+&#038;bg=ffffff&#038;fg=000&#038;s=0" alt="F_n = &#92;dfrac 1{&#92;sqrt 5}&#92;Big(&#92;Big(&#92;dfrac{1+&#92;sqrt 5}2 &#92;Big)^n - &#92;Big(&#92;dfrac{1-&#92;sqrt 5}2 &#92;Big)^n&#92;Big) &#92; " title="F_n = &#92;dfrac 1{&#92;sqrt 5}&#92;Big(&#92;Big(&#92;dfrac{1+&#92;sqrt 5}2 &#92;Big)^n - &#92;Big(&#92;dfrac{1-&#92;sqrt 5}2 &#92;Big)^n&#92;Big) &#92; " class="latex" /></p>
